<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blood Donation Confirmation - JeevanSetu</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .status {
            color: #fff;
            width: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            animation: blink 2s infinite;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #2b3a42;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #f4f3f3;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #2b3a42;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #ef5b5b;
            text-align: center;
        }

        img {
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #ef5b5b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dl5xf6aqa/image/upload/e_improve:outdoor/m8xgcg32qncggnpg4bob" height="100px"
                width="400px" alt="JeevanSetu Logo" />
            <h1>Blood Donation Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
                <p>Thank you for being a part of JeevanSetu and for your generous blood donation.</p>
                <p>Here are your donation details:</p>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <p><strong>Name:</strong>
                    <%= name %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong>
                    <%= email %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Tel:</strong>
                    <%= tel %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong>
                    <%= address %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Blood Group:</strong>
                    <%= bloodgroup %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Any Disease in Blood:</strong>
                    <%= diseases %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Weight:</strong>
                    <%= weight %> kg
                </p>
                <p><strong>Blood Pressure:</strong>
                    <%= bloodpressure %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Age:</strong>
                    <%= age %> years
                </p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong>
                    <%= date %>
                </p>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <p>Here are the details of nearby donation centers for your reference:</p>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Red Cross Blood Donation Center</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> July 20, 2024</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM</p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 MG Road, Bengaluru</p>
                <p>Contact Numbers:</p>
                <ul>
                <li>(+91) 456-789-0123</li>
                <li>(+91) 567-890-1234</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="divider"></div>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Community Health Center</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> July 22, 2024</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> 2:00 PM</p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 456 Anna Salai, Chennai</p>
                <p>Contact Numbers:</p>
                <ul>
                <li>(+91) 123-456-7890</li>
                <li>(+91) 234-567-8901</li>
                </ul>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1720957791/hero1_trpojy.jpg"
                alt="Blood Donation" height="250px" width="500px" />
            <h3>Note:</h3>
            <p>If you did not apply for blood donation, please contact us immediately at <a
                    href="mailto:support@jeevansetu.com">support@jeevansetu.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@jeevansetu.com"
                    class="footer-link">support@jeevansetu.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>